## Legacy reference site — read-only, for faithful-rebuild verification only

Hosted DEV deployment of the legacy Portal Dibujando (see
`.claude/dev/docs/legacy-app-runbook.md`). `legacy-ui-shot.mjs` reads these from the environment.
**Never write to this site — read-only reference only.**

```env
LEGACY_APP_URL=https://<hosted-dev-app>.azurewebsites.net
LEGACY_APP_EMAIL=<test-account-email>
LEGACY_APP_PASSWORD=<test-account-password>
```

## Executor — opencode-kimi

`opencode` manages its own model auth outside this repo; no Foundry-style credentials block is
needed here for the `opencode-kimi` executor.
